[30;1m171 | [0m[35mdef _temporary_keychain():[0m
[30;1m172 | [0m[35m    """[0m
[30;1m173 | [0m[35m    This function creates a temporary Mac keychain that we can use to work with[0m
[30;1m174 | [0m[35m    credentials. This keychain uses a one-time password and a temporary file to[0m

[30;1m269 | [0m[35m        """ Sleep between retry attempts.[0m
[30;1m270 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m271 | [0m[35m        This method will respect a server's ``Retry-After`` response header[0m
